title: Duo partner in high bronze or low silver.

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: Recently i have been one tricking yi in the jungle. I am looking for someone who can help duo carry late game if i was to camp their lane. Mid or top would be best for this.

replies.body: Just a tip, if you're looking to camp someone yi probably isn't the best pick, but its bronze so I guess anything can work.
